164
00:09:12,700 --> 00:09:14,500
Come and get it if you can hold it.

165
00:09:15,710 --> 00:09:16,440
Don't worry.

166
00:09:17,070 --> 00:09:18,550
To hold the Wangshu Sword,

167
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:21,350
