180
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:52,310
Lingsha.

181
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:54,250
Don't move.

182
00:09:55,790 --> 00:09:57,390
I'm gonna give you the sword.

183
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:27,640
Lingsha.

184
00:10:30,210 --> 00:10:30,850
Lingsha.

