186
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:48,830
Lingsha.

187
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:01,820
I've always been a man of my word.

188
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,850
The spiritual power of this purple crystal

189
00:11:03,850 --> 00:11:07,250
