193
00:11:22,610 --> 00:11:24,580
This is yours.

194
00:11:26,270 --> 00:11:27,530
Thank you, Lord Beike.

195
00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:29,180
Feng Xie,

196
00:11:29,590 --> 00:11:31,520
