200
00:11:44,070 --> 00:11:46,040
I can destroy the Wangshu Sword.

201
00:12:02,970 --> 00:12:03,770
Lingsha.

202
00:12:04,420 --> 00:12:05,060
Lingsha.

203
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:06,780
